data.description: Welcome to your dream home blocks from the historical Suffolk district! This charming 3-bedroom, 2 full bath front porch colonial is bursting with potential and is just waiting for your personal touch.A completely renovated kitchen with stainless steel looking appliances and stunning granite counter tops create an atmosphere of contemporary elegance. A spacious and open floor plan that is great for entertaining family and friends. The abundance of natural light with replacement vinyl windows.The expansive backyard with shed offers endless possibilities.  This property is an incredible opportunity to turn your vision into reality. Sold in "as is" condition, this home has all the bones to become your dream home with just a little bit of TLC. Unleash your creativity and let your imagination run wild as you transform this diamond in the rough into a true gem.
